---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import jayAuthor from "../assets/images/jay-profile.png";

const personJsonLd = JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Person",
  "name": "Jay Vergara",
  "url": "https://leadhuman.ai/about/",
  "jobTitle": "L&D Strategist",
  "worksFor": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Peak Potential Consulting" },
  "sameAs": [
    "https://linkedin.com/in/vergarajay/",
    "https://www.youtube.com/@leadhumanai",
    "https://www.tiktok.com/@leadhuman.ai"
  ],
  "knowsAbout": ["Leadership Development", "AI", "Cross-Cultural Communication"],
  "image": "https://leadhuman.ai" + jayAuthor.src
});
---

<BaseLayout title="About Jay Vergara, L&D Leader in Tokyo" description="About Jay Vergara — L&D strategist, cross-cultural communication specialist, and AI builder based in Tokyo. Partner at Peak Potential Consulting.">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={personJsonLd} slot="head" />
  <article class="max-w-3xl">

    <!-- Hero: Name + Image side by side -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-center sm:items-start mb-12">
      <div class="about-image-wrap relative w-[200px] sm:w-[220px] shrink-0">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded" style="aspect-ratio: 3/4;">
          <Image
            src={jayAuthor}
            alt="Jay Vergara"
            width={440}
            height={587}
            format="webp"
            quality={80}
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
            style="object-position: 50% 15%;"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 text-center sm:text-left">
        <p class="text-ivy font-medium italic mb-3" style="font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.35rem);">
          Lead&nbsp;humanly. Learn&nbsp;constantly. Build&nbsp;with&nbsp;AI.
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-heading mb-4" style="line-height: 1.1;">
          Jay Vergara
        </h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted tracking-wide uppercase mb-4">
          L&D Strategist · Leadership Development · AI Trainer<br />
          Tokyo, Japan · Vancouver, Canada
        </p>
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
          I grew up in Vancouver, B.C. and I've been living in Tokyo for over a decade now. Came thinking I'd stay a year or two and then... well, you know how that goes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Career story -->
    <div class="space-y-4 text-body leading-relaxed mb-10">
      <p>
        I've spent most of my career in learning and development. Indeed, Rakuten, TELUS, Yellow Pages. Building training programs and leading L&D teams and trying to figure out why most corporate learning doesn't actually stick.
      </p>
      <p>
        These days I run <a href="https://peakpotentialconsulting.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">Peak Potential Consulting</a> with my business partner Matt Gates. We help companies build leaders, teams, and learning cultures that work across borders.
      </p>
      <p>
        I also can't stop thinking about AI. Not in the "robots are coming for your job" way but in the "this changes everything about how we develop people and I want to be figuring it out" way. I use AI every single day to run the business, write content, pursue my MBA at <a href="https://www.globis.ac.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">GLOBIS University</a>, and build systems I couldn't have built alone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-10 divider-gradient" />

    <!-- What I do — expertise areas -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-heading">What I Actually Do</h2>
    <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
      I wear a few hats and they overlap more than you'd expect. Here's where I spend most of my time.
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-4 mb-6">
      <div class="bg-surface border border-card-border border-l-4 border-l-sky-700 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading mb-2">AI for HR, L&D, and Business</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          I build AI systems into my actual work. Not demos and not proofs of concept but real tools I use every day. Content pipelines, knowledge management systems, coaching assistants, and workflow automation for L&D teams. But it goes beyond HR and learning. I teach professionals how to use the AI tools they actually need for their work, whether that's automating reports, building internal tools, or just getting better at prompting. The goal is always the same: make the technology work for you so you can focus on the parts that need a human.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface border border-card-border border-l-4 border-l-emerald-800 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading mb-2">Learning & Development Strategy</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          I've built onboarding programs, designed instructional content, run learning measurement initiatives, and led L&D teams at companies with thousands of employees. The question I keep coming back to: why does most corporate training not change behavior? I write about what I've learned trying to answer that and the frameworks that actually work.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface border border-card-border border-l-4 border-l-orange-700 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading mb-2">Cross-Cultural Business Communication</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          A decade in Tokyo working across Japanese, North American, and Southeast Asian business cultures taught me things no textbook covers. I write about navigating high-context and low-context communication, running meetings across cultures, and the translation gaps that cause real problems in global teams. If you've ever had a meeting where everyone nodded and nothing happened, I've been there.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface border border-card-border border-l-4 border-l-emerald-800 rounded-lg p-5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading mb-2">Leadership & Manager Development</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          I design and deliver leadership development programs for first-time managers and senior leaders. That includes coaching frameworks, giving and receiving feedback, building psychological safety, and the messy human stuff that makes or breaks a team. Most of my work here is with global organizations where the people doing the leading are spread across cultures, time zones, and languages.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-10 divider-gradient" />

    <!-- What you'll find here — card layout -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-heading">What You'll Find on This Site</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
      <a href="/lead/" class="block bg-surface border border-card-border border-l-4 border-l-emerald-800 rounded-lg p-5 hover:bg-surface-light transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading mb-2">Lead Humanly</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Articles on leadership, cross-cultural communication, corporate learning strategy, and the human skills that matter more as AI takes over the rest.
        </p>
        <span class="text-xs text-ivy font-medium mt-3 inline-block">Read articles &rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/build/" class="block bg-surface border border-card-border border-l-4 border-l-sky-700 rounded-lg p-5 hover:bg-surface-light transition-colors">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading mb-2">Build with AI</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Hands-on tutorials for using AI in corporate training, talent development, and people operations. Real tools, real workflows, no hype.
        </p>
        <span class="text-xs text-ivy font-medium mt-3 inline-block">Read tutorials &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-body leading-relaxed mb-2">
      The thesis behind all of it is simple. The leaders who will matter most in the next decade are the ones who are deeply human AND technologically fluent. Not one or the other but both.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-10 divider-gradient" />

    <!-- Career Timeline -->
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-heading">Career Timeline</h2>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-8">Over a decade building training programs, developing leaders, and figuring out how organizations actually grow people.</p>

    <div class="career-timeline relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-divider">
      <!-- Peak Potential -->
      <div class="timeline-entry relative mb-8 animate-on-scroll" data-expandable>
        <div class="absolute -left-[calc(2rem+5px)] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-ivy border-2 border-ecru"></div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 mb-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading">Peak Potential Consulting</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-muted whitespace-nowrap">2022 &ndash; Present</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ivy mb-1">Partner &amp; Lead Learning Consultant &middot; 🇯🇵 Tokyo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Co-founded with Matt Gates, ACC. We work with companies across Japan and North America on leadership development, team building, and cross-cultural training.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Indeed -->
      <div class="timeline-entry relative mb-8 animate-on-scroll" data-expandable>
        <div class="absolute -left-[calc(2rem+5px)] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-ivy border-2 border-ecru"></div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 mb-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading">Indeed</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-muted whitespace-nowrap">2022 &ndash; 2025</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ivy mb-1">Lead Learning Partner &middot; 🇯🇵 Tokyo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Led AI learning programs, designed training for 800+ staff across APAC, coached internal facilitators, and built the AI Foundations program that expanded technical capability across the business.
        </p>
        <div class="timeline-details hidden mt-3 text-sm text-body leading-relaxed space-y-2 border-l-2 border-surface pl-4">
          <p>Rolled out AI Foundations and AI Coding Ambassador programs using Articulate 360 and Qualtrics, increasing employee confidence in AI adoption.</p>
          <p>Created multi-format learning assets (storyboards, scripts, training videos, podcasts) with Adobe Creative Suite.</p>
          <p>Moderated Coaching Cycles and Cluster Conversations to improve leadership and managerial skills across the region.</p>
          <p>Managed stakeholder relationships across Japan, Singapore, India, and Australia.</p>
        </div>
        <button class="timeline-toggle mt-2 text-xs text-ivy font-medium hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors cursor-pointer" aria-expanded="false">Show more &darr;</button>
      </div>

      <!-- Rakuten -->
      <div class="timeline-entry relative mb-8 animate-on-scroll" data-expandable>
        <div class="absolute -left-[calc(2rem+5px)] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-ivy border-2 border-ecru"></div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 mb-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading">Rakuten</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-muted whitespace-nowrap">2020 &ndash; 2022</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ivy mb-1">HR Development / Organizational Development &middot; 🇯🇵 Tokyo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Developed weekly culture training reaching 20,000+ team members across Japan, APAC, and EMEA. Launched and operated Business Do leadership training broadcast to 15,000 staff.
        </p>
        <div class="timeline-details hidden mt-3 text-sm text-body leading-relaxed space-y-2 border-l-2 border-surface pl-4">
          <p>Worked directly with the Rakuten Group CEO office and Kondo Marie on diversity and inclusion programming.</p>
          <p>Led the redevelopment and launch of Rakuten Philosophy Training for all Japan staff.</p>
          <p>Project managed Rakuten's internal 25th Anniversary portal.</p>
        </div>
        <button class="timeline-toggle mt-2 text-xs text-ivy font-medium hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors cursor-pointer" aria-expanded="false">Show more &darr;</button>
      </div>

      <!-- TELUS -->
      <div class="timeline-entry relative mb-8 animate-on-scroll" data-expandable>
        <div class="absolute -left-[calc(2rem+5px)] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-coral/60 border-2 border-ecru"></div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 mb-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading">TELUS</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-muted whitespace-nowrap">2018 &ndash; 2020</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ivy mb-1">Senior Learning Specialist &middot; 🇨🇦 Vancouver</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Facilitated 75+ training sessions for 1,200+ staff. Consulted on 30 home services projects and designed the training strategy for SmartHome Security from scratch.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Yellow Pages: Sales Training Manager -->
      <div class="timeline-entry relative mb-8 animate-on-scroll" data-expandable>
        <div class="absolute -left-[calc(2rem+5px)] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-coral/60 border-2 border-ecru"></div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 mb-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading">Yellow Pages</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-muted whitespace-nowrap">2015 &ndash; 2018</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ivy mb-1">Manager, Sales Training &amp; Enablement &middot; 🇨🇦 Vancouver</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Where I made the jump from sales into training. Facilitated 50 classes, designed 5 major national projects as a Master Trainer, spent 300+ hours in on-the-floor coaching, and built a 6-week onboarding program for Western Canada.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Yellow Pages: Media Account Consultant -->
      <div class="timeline-entry relative mb-8 animate-on-scroll" data-expandable>
        <div class="absolute -left-[calc(2rem+5px)] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-coral/60 border-2 border-ecru"></div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 mb-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading">Yellow Pages</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-muted whitespace-nowrap">2012 &ndash; 2015</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ivy mb-1">Media Account Consultant (Inside Sales) &middot; 🇨🇦 Vancouver</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Three years of inside sales before moving into training. Managed client relationships, designed advertising proposals, and became a Subject Matter Expert on digital advertising (SEM, SEO, Facebook, Creative Banner Ads). Also coached and onboarded new peers on the sales floor.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Coast Capital Savings -->
      <div class="timeline-entry relative mb-8 animate-on-scroll" data-expandable>
        <div class="absolute -left-[calc(2rem+5px)] top-1 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-coral/60 border-2 border-ecru"></div>
        <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-4 mb-1">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading">Coast Capital Savings</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-muted whitespace-nowrap">2011 &ndash; 2012</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ivy mb-1">Service Pro (Face to Face Sales) &middot; 🇨🇦 Vancouver</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Where it all started. Front-line banking sales, advising clients on financial products, hitting 110%+ of referral targets, and coaching peers on sales floor performance. The job that taught me I cared more about developing people than closing deals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Education & Credentials -->
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading mb-4">Education &amp; Credentials</h3>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6">
      <div class="credential-card bg-surface border border-card-border rounded-lg p-4 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ivy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 0 0-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0 1 12 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 0 1 8.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 0 0-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 0 0-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0 1 12 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0 1 10.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0 1 12 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 0 1 7.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0 1 12 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 0 0 6.75 15.75v-1.5" /></svg>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-heading"><a href="https://www.globis.ac.jp/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">GLOBIS University</a></p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted">Graduate School of Management &middot; Tokyo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body mt-1">Pre-MBA completed. MBA starting October 2026.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-card bg-surface border border-card-border rounded-lg p-4 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ivy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455 2.456Z" /></svg>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-heading"><a href="https://www.insights.com/products/insights-discovery/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">Insights Discovery</a></p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted">Accredited Practitioner</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body mt-1">Psychometric and behavioural profiling for team development and coaching.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-card bg-surface border border-card-border rounded-lg p-4 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ivy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z" /></svg>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-heading"><a href="https://intrivity.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-ivy hover:text-ivy-light transition-colors underline">Intrivity</a> Certified</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted">Communication &amp; Collaboration</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body mt-1">Certified facilitator for improving team communication and collaboration dynamics.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="credential-card bg-surface border border-card-border rounded-lg p-4 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-ivy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 8.511c.884.284 1.5 1.128 1.5 2.097v4.286c0 1.136-.847 2.1-1.98 2.193-.34.027-.68.052-1.02.072v3.091l-3-3c-1.354 0-2.694-.055-4.02-.163a2.115 2.115 0 0 1-.825-.242m9.345-8.334a2.126 2.126 0 0 0-.476-.095 48.64 48.64 0 0 0-8.048 0c-1.131.094-1.976 1.057-1.976 2.192v4.286c0 .837.46 1.58 1.155 1.951m9.345-8.334V6.637c0-1.621-1.152-3.026-2.76-3.235A48.455 48.455 0 0 0 11.25 3c-2.115 0-4.198.137-6.24.402-1.608.209-2.76 1.614-2.76 3.235v6.226c0 1.621 1.152 3.026 2.76 3.235.577.075 1.157.14 1.74.194V21l4.155-4.155" /></svg>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-heading">Languages</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted">Bilingual professional</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-body mt-1">English (native) / Japanese (studying for JLPT&nbsp;N2)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Personal -->
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-heading mb-4">When I'm Not Working</h3>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3 mb-6">
      <div class="hobby-card group bg-surface border border-card-border rounded-lg p-4 text-center animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full bg-ivy/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-ivy/20 transition-colors duration-200">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ivy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.182 15.182a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-6.364 0M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0ZM9.75 9.75c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75S9 10.164 9 9.75 9.168 9 9.375 9s.375.336.375.75Zm-.375 0h.008v.015h-.008V9.75Zm5.625 0c0 .414-.168.75-.375.75s-.375-.336-.375-.75.168-.75.375-.75.375.336.375.75Zm-.375 0h.008v.015h-.008V9.75Z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-heading">Dad</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">Priority number one</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hobby-card group bg-surface border border-card-border rounded-lg p-4 text-center animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-3 rounded-full bg-ivy/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-ivy/20 transition-colors duration-200">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ivy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.827 6.175A2.31 2.31 0 0 1 5.186 7.23c-.38.054-.757.112-1.134.175C2.999 7.58 2.25 8.507 2.25 9.574V18a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25h15A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21.75 18V9.574c0-1.067-.75-1.994-1.802-2.169a47.865 47.865 0 0 0-1.134-.175 2.31 2.31 0 0 1-1.64-1.055l-.822-1.316a2.192 2.192 0 0 0-1.736-1.039 48.774 48.774 0 0 0-5.232 0 2.192 2.192 0 0 0-1.736 1.039l-.821 1.316Z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 12.75a4.5 4.5 0 1 1-9 0 4.5 4.5 0 0 1 9 0ZM18.75 10.5h.008v.008h-.008V10.5Z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-heading">Photography</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-1">Landscape, street, portrait</p>
